    "It aims to assist educators in comprehensively understanding the effectiveness of diverse PBL methodologies.",
    "This understanding is crucial for the development of various dimensions of computational thinking, thereby providing valuable insights and guidance for future educational practices and research initiatives.",
    "As a key to future societal development, CT is receiving increasing attention globally, especially in the field of education.",
    "Studies suggest that encouragement for the creation of new teaching curricula (INTEF, 2018; Manches & Plowman, 2017; Micheuz, 2008), suited to different age groups and types of learning processes, is evident both at the level of educational policy and among academic researchers (Angeli & Valanides, 2020; Balanskat & Engelhardt, 2015; Brennan & Resnick, 2012).",
    "These fresh curriculum design concepts and practices have opened new pathways and models for learning CT in K-12 education, positively influencing the entire educational industry."
